<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:ddanda" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tribhu</hi>vanac—<note n="300-1">There is the figure of a lamp drawn in bold relief to the left of the first two lines.</note>
<lb n="2"/>ṟku yāṇṭu <num value="29">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 9</num> Āvatu Āṉi<unclear>mātam</unclear>—
